14:07.447 --> 14:09.249
but I could get
real money for this.

14:09.282 --> 14:11.218
Well, that could compromise
our investigation.

14:11.251 --> 14:13.620
I think maybe The Enquirer
would pay me for an interview.

14:13.653 --> 14:15.455
You could turn them down.

14:15.488 --> 14:17.657
That depends
how much they offer.

14:17.690 --> 14:19.359
Detective Munch.
Yes, sir?

14:19.392 --> 14:20.593
Take this young man
into custody

14:20.627 --> 14:21.594
as a material witness.

14:21.628 --> 14:22.529
Lock him up

14:22.562 --> 14:24.631
