He just did.

14:27.334 --> 14:28.401
BENSON:
Same M.O.

14:28.435 --> 14:30.070
Torn underwear
on the ground,

14:30.103 --> 14:31.438
and the smell of fuel oil.

14:31.471 --> 14:33.373
