to talk to you.

18:19.599 --> 18:21.268
Sean...

18:24.171 --> 18:25.738
( tires screeching )

18:25.772 --> 18:27.907
( horn honking )

18:27.940 --> 18:30.243
BENSON:
What are you
running from, Sean?

18:30.277 --> 18:32.245
We just want
to have a little chat.

18:32.279 --> 18:33.613
You're under arrest
for the murders

18:33.646 --> 18:35.315
of Tariq Assad and Mira Elbisi.

18:35.348 --> 18:36.549
