to do this.

18:36.583 --> 18:37.417
Just listen to me.

18:37.450 --> 18:39.252
You have the right to remain...
Shut up!

18:39.286 --> 18:40.620
You have the right
to remain silent.

18:40.653 --> 18:41.821
