can and will be
used against you...

18:43.923 --> 18:45.692
But you're like me;
I know you are, man!

18:45.725 --> 18:47.260
You have the right
to an attorney.

18:49.629 --> 18:50.863
Been in some
trouble before,

18:50.897 --> 18:52.399
so when I saw
you two coming,

18:52.432 --> 18:53.333
