to our way of life.

19:32.439 --> 19:33.740
Way of life?

19:33.773 --> 19:34.874
Which way is that?

19:34.907 --> 19:36.843
Freedom, democracy.

19:38.845 --> 19:41.214
If these people don't believe
in those things,

19:41.248 --> 19:44.917
and they get money for terrorism
from overseas...

19:44.951 --> 19:49.256
well, somebody ought
to kill them, right?

19:52.325 --> 19:53.526
Almost dissociating,

19:53.560 --> 19:55.328
as if this
isn't about him.

19:55.362 --> 19:57.530
Sounds like he wants Olivia's
and Elliot's approval.

19:57.564 --> 19:58.631
Well, it makes
you wonder

19:58.665 --> 20:00.733
