he really wants.

20:00.767 --> 20:03.403
Fuel oil in Sean's truck
is a perfect match

20:03.436 --> 20:04.537
to the victims.

20:04.571 --> 20:06.973
36 million gallons sold
every ten seconds.

20:07.006 --> 20:09.942
The dumbest lawyer in town
can do an O.J. DNA with it.

20:09.976 --> 20:11.278
The lab says

20:11.311 --> 20:12.879
