with benzene.

20:12.912 --> 20:14.881
Munch and Fin
are going to need
a search warrant

20:14.914 --> 20:15.882
for the kid's
apartment.

20:15.915 --> 20:17.284
It's done. He saying anything?

20:17.317 --> 20:18.418
HUANG:
Not directly.

20:18.451 --> 20:19.752
