they'd never heard of my son.

20:51.418 --> 20:52.819
He's at our
precinct, ma'am.

20:52.852 --> 20:53.986
You have to stop.

20:54.020 --> 20:55.355
You have to leave right now.

20:55.388 --> 20:56.889
You'd better look
at that search warrant.

20:56.923 --> 20:58.325
You don't stay out
of our way,

20:58.358 --> 20:59.892
