to arrest you, too.

20:59.926 --> 21:00.927
MUNCH:
Check this out.

21:00.960 --> 21:02.395
The Citizen's
Survival Manual

21:02.429 --> 21:03.530
published by

21:03.563 --> 21:04.797
The White People's Press.

21:04.831 --> 21:07.667
"Chapter Six: Fires
and How to Start Them."

21:07.700 --> 21:09.936
Why do these publishers
always have post office boxes

21:09.969 --> 21:11.604
and not real addresses?

21:11.638 --> 21:13.540
