21:13.573 --> 21:15.675
Cleaning fluid.

21:15.708 --> 21:16.943
Ingredients:

21:16.976 --> 21:18.845
dichloramethane

21:18.878 --> 21:20.880
and- what do you know--
benzene.

21:24.884 --> 21:26.853
Sean, you got some decisions
