to understand?

21:35.862 --> 21:36.963
Talk to me, talk to me.

21:36.996 --> 21:38.698
What are they going
to understand?

21:38.731 --> 21:41.334
How in the hell did you
get yourself into this mess?

21:41.368 --> 21:42.835
I don't know.

21:42.869 --> 21:44.837
You come from
where I come from, and...

21:44.871 --> 21:46.105
( sighs )

21:46.138 --> 21:48.708
Thing's are supposed
to be different.

21:48.741 --> 21:50.710
I'm a real American.

21:50.743 --> 21:52.845
