22:09.862 --> 22:11.063
what I know.

22:11.097 --> 22:13.566
How much longer are you going
to keep me here?

22:13.600 --> 22:15.935
It's entirely up to you.

22:15.968 --> 22:17.937
See, you just don't get it,
