22:17.970 --> 22:19.739
( sighs )

22:19.772 --> 22:21.408
Things were different
when I grew up.

22:21.441 --> 22:23.009
You didn't have these... people.

22:23.042 --> 22:25.111
Look, there's always
been foreigners here.

22:25.144 --> 22:25.912
