Sisters of Mercy.

23:36.716 --> 23:37.817
You go to college?

23:37.850 --> 23:39.218
Yeah, I went
to night school.

23:39.251 --> 23:41.888
Just got out of the Marines,

23:41.921 --> 23:43.923
but, uh, I got my BA.

23:45.725 --> 23:46.826
So, now, how come

23:46.859 --> 23:48.094
you had to go
into the service

23:48.127 --> 23:49.696
instead of straight to college?

23:49.729 --> 23:50.697
My dad was a cop.

23:50.730 --> 23:51.698
I got two sisters,

23:51.731 --> 23:53.199
