exactly my point.

23:57.737 --> 23:58.705
I didn't get to go myself

23:58.738 --> 24:00.840
'cause all the places were
taken up by Arabs,

24:00.873 --> 24:02.642
who come over here
with their oil money,

24:02.675 --> 24:04.611
