24:23.295 --> 24:26.666
What do you think?

24:29.769 --> 24:31.871
See, you don't get it.

24:35.908 --> 24:38.010
He gets it.

24:42.181 --> 24:45.184
Gas chromo on
the benzene was
a dead-on match

24:45.217 --> 24:47.754
to the residue on
both the victims.

24:47.787 --> 24:48.888
This going anywhere?

24:48.921 --> 24:50.289
No, I thought he'd crack.

24:50.322 --> 24:51.958
He's having too good a time.

24:51.991 --> 24:54.026
I can try and go
and light him up.

24:54.060 --> 24:55.695
It's been four-and-a-half hours.

24:55.728 --> 24:57.897
Knock yourself out.

25:01.267 --> 25:04.937
Detective Tutuola,
Sean Webster.

25:06.238 --> 25:09.241
And what's he doing here?

25:09.275 --> 25:12.011
You invited him?

25:12.044 --> 25:14.647
You don't like me very much,
do you?

25:14.681 --> 25:15.548
BENSON:
Actually,

25:15.582 --> 25:17.149
I'm not all that invested
either way.

25:17.183 --> 25:18.150
What do you
see in her?

25:18.184 --> 25:19.018
You know
what I see?

25:19.051 --> 25:20.820
I think she's got
some color in her.

25:20.853 --> 25:23.122
What's in you?

25:23.155 --> 25:25.291
Arab? Raghead?

25:25.324 --> 25:27.059
Oh, and you look it, too, boy.

25:27.093 --> 25:29.929
You got some
raghead in you?

25:29.962 --> 25:31.330
In Africa, folks moved around,

25:31.363 --> 25:33.132
intermixing for thousands
of years.

25:33.165 --> 25:34.300
I could be part Arab.

25:34.333 --> 25:35.935
Oh.

25:35.968 --> 25:36.903
That would explain

25:36.936 --> 25:40.206
why your coon brothers went
to the enemy.

25:40.239 --> 25:41.741
Black Muslims.

25:41.774 --> 25:44.343
Traitors to the American people.

25:44.376 --> 25:46.345
You can call me anything
you want, Sean.

25:46.378 --> 25:47.714
Coon, traitor,

25:47.747 --> 25:49.916
raghead, towelhead.

25:49.949 --> 25:52.318
I got some words for you:

25:52.351 --> 25:54.086
killer, psycho.

25:54.120 --> 25:56.355
Hey...

25:56.388 --> 25:58.357
I'm no psycho.

25:58.390 --> 26:00.793
You burned two innocent people
to death.

26:00.827 --> 26:01.794
They weren't innocent!

26:01.828 --> 26:04.096
They had to die,
or they're going to kill us all.

26:04.130 --> 26:05.698
Well, who was Mira Elbisi
gonna kill?

26:05.732 --> 26:06.733
She was working for peace.

26:06.766 --> 26:08.901
I didn't want to kill her!

26:19.145 --> 26:22.849
You tore up that innocent woman
with that pipe,

26:22.882 --> 26:24.851
then you burned her alive.

26:24.884 --> 26:27.086
You're sick.

26:29.421 --> 26:32.792
She said
that she was a good American,

26:32.825 --> 26:35.094
and that raghead said
that he was our friend.

26:36.663 --> 26:38.130
They're all liars.

26:38.164 --> 26:39.398
We have to stop them,

26:39.431 --> 26:41.701
or they're going to kill us all!

26:46.739 --> 26:48.775
You okay?

26:48.808 --> 26:51.010
I'll take words anytime
over being raped with a pipe.

26:51.043 --> 26:52.812
You've got thicker
skin than me.

26:52.845 --> 26:53.946
Couple hundred years,

26:53.980 --> 26:56.215
races will be so mixed up,
it won't matter.

26:56.248 --> 26:58.284
No one will know
what color anyone is.

26:58.317 --> 26:59.786
He got to you.

26:59.819 --> 27:01.821
A little.

27:01.854 --> 27:03.890
He thought he'd rattle
me by calling me an Arab,

27:03.923 --> 27:05.024
but the truth is,

27:05.057 --> 27:06.859
I don't know anything
about my father.

27:06.893 --> 27:08.961
Race and color are the
least of my questions.

27:08.995 --> 27:10.396
Probation report.

27:10.429 --> 27:11.964
Sean Webster, aged 16,

27:11.998 --> 27:13.766
attacked a Pakistani kid
at school.

27:13.800 --> 27:15.768
Tried as an adult,
sentenced as a juvenile.

27:15.802 --> 27:17.003
No time served.

27:17.036 --> 27:18.237
Father died when he was ten.

27:18.270 --> 27:19.772
Mother had a nervous breakdown,

27:19.806 --> 27:21.874
had to move out of the house
from Long Island.

27:21.908 --> 27:23.175
Brought the kid into the city.

27:23.209 --> 27:25.177
He's been in and out
of trouble ever since.

27:25.211 --> 27:27.246
You want us to feel
sorry for him?

27:27.279 --> 27:29.448
Oh, no. He's a racist
son of a bitch.

27:29.481 --> 27:31.784
With a damn good lawyer.

27:33.052 --> 27:34.386
The confession's inadmissible.

27:34.420 --> 27:35.454
He was Mirandized.

27:35.487 --> 27:36.789
He never asked for a lawyer.

27:36.823 --> 27:38.190
You can stop
grandstanding, Oliver.

27:38.224 --> 27:39.458
This isn't a
press conference.

27:39.491 --> 27:41.393
You kept him hidden
from his own mother.

27:41.427 --> 27:42.929
CRAGEN:
No, no. Our
detectives

27:42.962 --> 27:43.930
told his mother we had him.

27:43.963 --> 27:46.132
Yeah, he was offered his
phone call. He declined.

27:46.165 --> 27:48.234
The confession was provoked.
I'll get it excluded.

27:48.267 --> 27:50.302
NOVAK:
Well, there's not much
law on provocation.

27:50.336 --> 27:52.104
And considering
how wired your client is,

27:52.138 --> 27:53.305
I'd say, he provokes easily.

27:53.339 --> 27:54.673
The confession will stick.

27:56.242 --> 27:58.911
Maybe you're right.

27:58.945 --> 28:00.913
See you in court.

28:06.786 --> 28:08.087
I've seen that smile.

28:08.120 --> 28:10.289
Usually before he demolishes
the prosecution's case.

28:10.322 --> 28:13.492
How did that kid's mother find
Oliver Gates?

28:13.525 --> 28:16.228
He's one of the major opponents
of the hate-crimes statute.

28:16.262 --> 28:17.964
Well, he picked
the right case.

28:17.997 --> 28:19.365
Well, we'll deny him
the pleasure.

28:19.398 --> 28:21.067
I don't need
a sentencing enhancement.

28:21.100 --> 28:22.835
We'll convict Webster
for both killings.

28:22.869 --> 28:24.103
He does consecutive time.

28:24.136 --> 28:26.038
It's 50 years before
he sees a parole board.

28:26.072 --> 28:28.440
My opinion?

28:28.474 --> 28:30.376
You need a hate-crimes charge.

28:30.409 --> 28:31.443
It goes to motive.

28:31.477 --> 28:35.047
I think we should prosecute
action, not thought.

28:35.081 --> 28:36.248
Webster killed out of hate.

28:36.282 --> 28:37.316
That matters.

28:37.349 --> 28:38.317
Okay, you tell me.

28:38.350 --> 28:39.886
Does that mean

28:39.919 --> 28:42.254
a black man who kills a Klansman
does additional time?

28:42.288 --> 28:43.856
Or a gay man
who kills a homophobe?

28:43.890 --> 28:45.291
I mean, where do we draw
the line?

28:45.324 --> 28:46.859
Hate crimes incite
other people.

28:46.893 --> 28:47.994
( phone ringing )

28:48.027 --> 28:49.128
It's a kind of terror.

28:49.161 --> 28:50.997
We use the statute
to make a point.

28:51.030 --> 28:52.264
( phone continues ringing )

28:52.298 --> 28:54.433
Cragen.

28:55.434 --> 28:57.937
Yeah. We'll be right there.

28:59.939 --> 29:02.008
Sean Webster just killed
a Muslim prisoner

29:02.041 --> 29:04.010
at Central Booking.

29:04.043 --> 29:05.411
MAN:
Webster was in the pens,

29:05.444 --> 29:08.014
waiting for arraignment
when he just flipped out.

29:08.047 --> 29:09.415
He stomped the Arab guy
into a pulp.

29:09.448 --> 29:10.817
Why didn't you
segregate him?

29:10.850 --> 29:11.984
He's booked for two murders.

29:12.018 --> 29:13.419
We didn't know
about a racial angle.

29:13.452 --> 29:15.788
Nobody said squat, okay?

29:15.822 --> 29:17.423
Your lawyer's going
to be pissed, Sean.

29:17.456 --> 29:19.058
You just convicted yourself.

29:19.091 --> 29:22.128
One less Arab,
one less terrorist.

29:22.161 --> 29:24.296
GATES:
Sean, seal your lips,
not another word.

29:24.330 --> 29:27.099
Actually, my client just proved
my theory correct.

29:27.133 --> 29:28.300
NOVAK:
What?

29:28.334 --> 29:29.368
Another murder
gets him off?

29:29.401 --> 29:30.369
No. It gets him sent

29:30.402 --> 29:31.303
to a mental hospital

29:31.337 --> 29:33.239
for the treatment
he so desperately needs.

29:33.272 --> 29:34.440
An insanity defense?

29:34.473 --> 29:35.942
You've got no grounds.

29:35.975 --> 29:37.009
Sure I do.

29:37.043 --> 29:38.077
His genes.

29:38.110 --> 29:39.578
The motion will be filed
tomorrow.

29:39.611 --> 29:42.381
Sean Webster is biologically
and genetically predisposed

29:42.414 --> 29:43.515
to hatred and violence.

29:43.549 --> 29:45.351
He had no control
over his actions.

29:45.384 --> 29:47.353
It'll never fly.

29:47.386 --> 29:48.855
You put a man's genes on trial,

29:48.888 --> 29:50.857
nobody will ever be responsible
for anything.

29:51.891 --> 29:53.960
It's the ultimate defense.

30:02.468 --> 30:04.170
NOVAK:
Your Honor, this
defense is absurd.

30:04.203 --> 30:06.072
The defendant sodomized
and burned two people

30:06.105 --> 30:08.908
and beat a prisoner to death.

30:08.941 --> 30:11.443
His guilt cannot be determined
by his genes.

30:11.477 --> 30:13.479
Are you citing the
law, Counselor,

30:13.512 --> 30:15.314
or is this just
your opinion?

30:15.347 --> 30:16.282
The law is clear.

30:16.315 --> 30:18.918
New York doesn't have
an insanity defense

30:18.951 --> 30:20.452
of "irresistible impulse."

30:20.486 --> 30:21.888
We ask that it
be excluded.

30:21.921 --> 30:22.955
Thank you, Ms. Novak.

30:22.989 --> 30:24.190
Proceed.

30:24.223 --> 30:26.025
GATES:
Thank you, Your Honor.

30:26.058 --> 30:27.459
My client, Sean Webster,

30:27.493 --> 30:30.562
believes that Muslims
are a danger to our society,

30:30.596 --> 30:32.331
and therefore,
he's driven to kill them.

30:32.364 --> 30:33.866
Now, we will prove

30:33.900 --> 30:35.601
that he's not responsible
for these crimes

30:35.634 --> 30:37.203
because he was born

30:37.236 --> 30:39.438
with hatred and violence
hard-wired into his brain.

30:39.471 --> 30:40.539
Your Honor,
the defendant

30:40.572 --> 30:41.607
ran from the police.

30:41.640 --> 30:42.875
He knew right from wrong.

30:42.909 --> 30:43.876
That negates

30:43.910 --> 30:44.977
a mental disease
defense.

30:45.011 --> 30:46.078
Michigan v. Carpenter.

30:46.112 --> 30:47.046
Not wanting to be caught

30:47.079 --> 30:49.181
is different
than knowing right from wrong.

30:49.215 --> 30:51.450
And what better proof
he can't control his actions

30:51.483 --> 30:53.485
in killing another inmate
while awaiting two trials?

30:53.519 --> 30:55.221
JUDGE:
You know, you
haven't convinced me

30:55.254 --> 30:56.288
that biology is the issue

30:56.322 --> 30:59.658
or that it's proper for me
to allow this defense.

30:59.691 --> 31:00.960
U.S. v. Robertson.

31:00.993 --> 31:02.561
The trial judge must consider

31:02.594 --> 31:05.231
the defendant's ability
to control himself.

31:05.264 --> 31:06.632
I know the case, Counselor.

31:06.665 --> 31:10.236
I went to law school, too.

31:10.269 --> 31:12.038
I'll review
your scientific evidence.

31:12.071 --> 31:15.074
And I presume you have

31:15.107 --> 31:17.143
a bang-up expert witness.

31:17.176 --> 31:18.644
The esteemed Dr. Emily Sopher,

31:18.677 --> 31:21.447
Chair of Neurobiology
at the Mid-Hudson Institute.

31:21.480 --> 31:23.515
JUDGE:
Documents in my
chambers, 48 hours.

31:23.549 --> 31:25.317
You'll make your
witness available

31:25.351 --> 31:26.652
to the District Attorney.

31:26.685 --> 31:28.187
( gavel bangs )

31:28.220 --> 31:29.621
The whole defense is bogus.

31:29.655 --> 31:31.523
The judge should've
dismissed it.

31:31.557 --> 31:32.658
He still might.

31:32.691 --> 31:33.625
Casey!

31:33.659 --> 31:36.128
Now, this is gonna be a blast,
don't you think?

31:36.162 --> 31:37.396
I think it's a bad joke.

31:37.429 --> 31:40.266
Your client killed that inmate
just to make himself look crazy.

31:40.299 --> 31:41.567
No, he can't control

31:41.600 --> 31:44.270
his genetic predisposition
to hatred.

31:44.303 --> 31:46.305
Why are you doing this,
Oliver?

31:46.338 --> 31:47.406
It's the next frontier.

31:47.439 --> 31:48.674
I like being
on the cutting edge.

31:48.707 --> 31:50.542
You like being
in the spotlight.

31:50.576 --> 31:52.678
That, too.

31:52.711 --> 31:55.314
Why, it must be genetic.

31:56.348 --> 31:59.285
You think his expert
can convince a jury?

31:59.318 --> 32:00.987
Sopher's a world-class
neurobiologist.

32:01.020 --> 32:03.022
There's no telling what
they're going to think.

32:03.055 --> 32:04.156
You talk to Sopher.

32:04.190 --> 32:05.491
See what you think.

32:06.525 --> 32:08.560
Read the research
on brain chemistry.

32:08.594 --> 32:10.296
Multiple studies, not just mine.

32:10.329 --> 32:12.431
Genotypes that cause low levels

32:12.464 --> 32:15.434
of monoamine oxidase A
predict violence.

32:15.467 --> 32:18.004
Maybe violence is
genetically influenced,

32:18.037 --> 32:20.172
but hatred is a
learned behavior.

32:20.206 --> 32:22.074
Actually,
my research shows

32:22.108 --> 32:24.443
that emotions
are genetically determined.

32:24.476 --> 32:27.579
Someday we'll treat
the Sean Websters of the world

32:27.613 --> 32:29.248
with gene therapy

32:29.281 --> 32:31.150
before they commit
terrible crimes.

32:31.183 --> 32:34.120
You start treating people
you think will be criminals,

32:34.153 --> 32:36.288
you turn psychiatry
into social control.

32:36.322 --> 32:39.391
All due respect, Dr. Huang,
you're living in the past.

32:39.425 --> 32:41.027
You're living in the future.

32:41.060 --> 32:43.462
You might be able
to prove your theories then,

32:43.495 --> 32:45.331
but you can't do it now.

32:45.364 --> 32:46.598
I can convince a jury.

32:46.632 --> 32:48.400
Do you think
that a courtroom

32:48.434 --> 32:51.103
is the right place
to test-drive your ideas?

32:51.137 --> 32:52.204
Where should we do it?

32:52.238 --> 32:55.074
At some academic conference
where no one'll notice?

32:55.107 --> 32:58.377
You might not want to testify
after you read my research.

33:01.680 --> 33:05.684
GATES:
Dr. Sopher, are hatred

33:05.717 --> 33:08.220
and racist violence
mental diseases?

33:08.254 --> 33:12.224
Yes. They're caused by
genetic abnormalities
in the brain.

33:12.258 --> 33:14.426
Where in the brain
does this occur?

33:14.460 --> 33:15.661
In the prefrontal cortex

33:15.694 --> 33:18.097
which controls emotions
and which is smaller

33:18.130 --> 33:20.299
in people convicted
of violent hate crimes.

33:20.332 --> 33:23.769
Dr. Sopher, were you able to
examine Sean Webster's brain?

33:23.802 --> 33:25.371
Yes, first slide please.

33:25.404 --> 33:26.638
( machine clicks )

33:26.672 --> 33:28.374
These images are
called PET scans.

33:28.407 --> 33:31.110
The one on the left shows
a normal prefrontal cortex.

33:31.143 --> 33:33.445
On the right
is Sean Webster's.

33:33.479 --> 33:35.347
His is abnormally small.

33:35.381 --> 33:38.317
More important, violent
people have more activity

33:38.350 --> 33:41.353
than normal people
in another section
of the brain.

33:41.387 --> 33:43.255
It's called the subcortex.

33:43.289 --> 33:44.390
How can you tell?

33:44.423 --> 33:45.624
Well, for example,

33:45.657 --> 33:47.359
here's a scan of the subcortex

33:47.393 --> 33:48.794
of a neo-Nazi skinhead

33:48.827 --> 33:51.397
who was convicted
of attacking Jews.

33:51.430 --> 33:55.301
This is his subcortex after
he hears the word "Jew."

33:55.334 --> 33:56.735
Note how it lights up.

33:56.768 --> 33:59.671
Did you perform this
test on Sean Webster?

33:59.705 --> 34:01.640
Yes.

34:01.673 --> 34:03.509
His subcortex lit
up the same way

34:03.542 --> 34:05.277
when he heard
the word "Arab."

34:05.311 --> 34:07.279
Your conclusion,
Dr. Sopher?

34:07.313 --> 34:09.215
The mere mention of Arabs

34:09.248 --> 34:13.152
puts Sean Webster into a state
of extreme hatred and violence.

34:13.185 --> 34:14.553
Thank you.

34:14.586 --> 34:16.555
Your witness.

34:16.588 --> 34:20.159
Can you tell by looking
at pictures of people's brains

34:20.192 --> 34:22.294
whether they'll kill
other people?

34:22.328 --> 34:24.563
That's difficult to say.

34:24.596 --> 34:26.765
Your Honor?

34:26.798 --> 34:28.300
Answer the question, Dr. Sopher.

34:28.334 --> 34:30.869
With enough time
and sufficient PET scans,

34:30.902 --> 34:35.174
yes, I'll eventually be able to
predict who will become violent.

34:35.207 --> 34:36.708
"Eventually predict"?

34:36.742 --> 34:38.310
Eventually.

34:38.344 --> 34:40.078
But not now?

34:41.913 --> 34:44.750
No.

34:44.783 --> 34:45.884
HUANG:
I turned to colleagues

34:45.917 --> 34:47.453
at the Ranney
Psychiatric Institute

34:47.486 --> 34:49.121
to replicate
Dr. Sopher's experiments.

34:49.155 --> 34:51.123
Tell us what you found,
Dr. Huang.

34:51.157 --> 34:52.758
We interviewed
several people.

34:52.791 --> 34:55.727
Number one is the PET
scan of an orthodox rabbi.

34:55.761 --> 34:58.597
We showed him that
picture of Nazi officers.

34:58.630 --> 35:02.201
His subcortex responded
exactly like Sean Webster's.

35:02.234 --> 35:06.638
Number two is the subcortex
of an African-American minister.

35:06.672 --> 35:08.674
We showed him that picture
of the Ku Klux Klan

35:08.707 --> 35:09.875
at a rally burning a cross.

35:09.908 --> 35:12.211
So, both of these men

35:12.244 --> 35:14.480
have the same subcortical
activity as Sean Webster?

35:14.513 --> 35:16.348
That's correct.

35:16.382 --> 35:19.418
What do these results
mean to you, Doctor?

35:19.451 --> 35:21.753
That even if behavior
is partly genetic,

35:21.787 --> 35:23.755
it's about our experiences,
also.

35:23.789 --> 35:27.793
After you're bitten by a dog,
you might not like them,

35:27.826 --> 35:30.429
but you weren't born
to hate them.

35:31.463 --> 35:33.499
Your witness.

35:33.532 --> 35:37.369
Dr. Huang, is high cholesterol
genetically caused?

35:37.403 --> 35:38.637
We think so.

35:38.670 --> 35:40.872
Can you identify the genes
which cause it?

35:40.906 --> 35:43.342
In the average patient, not yet.

35:43.375 --> 35:45.411
No. So, if I have
high cholesterol

35:45.444 --> 35:47.246
and I die of a heart attack

35:47.279 --> 35:49.915
it may have been
genetically predetermined?

35:49.948 --> 35:52.184
Yes.

35:52.218 --> 35:54.253
But you're saying
that Sean Webster,

35:54.286 --> 35:58.790
and not his genetic make-up,
is responsible for his violence?

35:58.824 --> 36:01.327
Dr. Huang?

36:01.360 --> 36:02.661
It's not that simple.

36:02.694 --> 36:04.196
Thank you.

36:04.230 --> 36:06.398
I was thinking the same thing.

36:06.432 --> 36:07.799
I wasn't finished.

36:07.833 --> 36:09.501
Dr. Sopher identifies
violent people

36:09.535 --> 36:11.237
after they've committed
hate crimes.

36:11.270 --> 36:12.971
That doesn't mean
she can predict violence

36:13.004 --> 36:14.206
based on their brain patterns.

36:14.240 --> 36:16.942
No more than you can predict
someone having a heart attack

36:16.975 --> 36:18.710
based solely
on their cholesterol level.

36:18.744 --> 36:21.747
But your rabbi or minister could
become violent at any moment.

36:21.780 --> 36:22.814
Any of us could.

36:22.848 --> 36:23.982
My point, thank you.

36:24.015 --> 36:26.718
That includes Sean Webster.

36:30.956 --> 36:33.692
When I was a kid, I
was always in trouble.

36:33.725 --> 36:36.695
The school sent me
to a therapist,

36:36.728 --> 36:38.564
but it never helped.

36:38.597 --> 36:40.966
What kind of trouble?

36:40.999 --> 36:42.934
Fights mostly.

36:42.968 --> 36:45.604
Who did you fight?

36:45.637 --> 36:46.838
Arabs.

36:46.872 --> 36:48.340
People like Tariq Assad

36:48.374 --> 36:50.008
and Mira Elbisi?

36:50.041 --> 36:51.877
Yeah.

36:52.911 --> 36:55.447
What made you choose them?

36:55.481 --> 36:59.418
I saw this poster for
a panel they were on.

36:59.451 --> 37:01.487
I went and I listened.

37:01.520 --> 37:04.990
You know, they say
that they're our friends.

37:05.023 --> 37:07.693
They're more dangerous
than the ones

37:07.726 --> 37:09.895
who admit they're our enemies.

37:09.928 --> 37:12.864
Did you hear voices telling you
to kill them?

37:12.898 --> 37:14.600
No, sir.

37:14.633 --> 37:16.001
Crazy people hear voices.

37:16.034 --> 37:17.769
I'm not crazy.

37:18.770 --> 37:22.474
But, still, you felt
you had to kill them.

37:22.508 --> 37:25.644
They hate and want to destroy
our country.

37:25.677 --> 37:29.448
Do you think killing people
is wrong?

37:29.481 --> 37:31.049
We kill people in wars,

37:31.082 --> 37:34.420
and we're at war
with these people, right?

37:34.453 --> 37:36.622
Thank you.

37:36.655 --> 37:37.889
Your witness.

37:37.923 --> 37:39.758
So you hate Muslims.

37:39.791 --> 37:43.028
Do you hate black people,
too, Sean?

37:43.061 --> 37:44.996
No, ma'am.

37:45.030 --> 37:48.767
Well, I mean, except
for the ones who are Muslims.

37:48.800 --> 37:51.770
Do you hate the Chinese,
Japanese?

37:51.803 --> 37:53.305
No, ma'am.

37:53.339 --> 37:55.707
So your hatred's
pretty specific.

37:55.741 --> 37:57.843
Muslims come here,

37:57.876 --> 38:02.648
and they study
engineering and aviation,

38:02.681 --> 38:04.916
and then they use it
to attack us,

38:04.950 --> 38:07.386
and we fought for them
in Bosnia,

38:07.419 --> 38:10.389
and my dad fought for them
in Desert Storm,

38:10.422 --> 38:12.458
and he died for his country.

38:12.491 --> 38:13.759
They killed your father?

38:13.792 --> 38:15.427
Muslims killed your father?

38:15.461 --> 38:17.062
And they turn around,
and they attack us!

38:17.095 --> 38:19.831
And they're gonna explode
chemical warfare in the subways!

38:19.865 --> 38:21.400
Sean!

38:21.433 --> 38:23.602
And poison our water supplies
and blow up bridges!

38:23.635 --> 38:25.003
Your Honor, may
we have a recess?

38:25.036 --> 38:27.873
JUDGE:
I'm going to recess
while the defendant

38:27.906 --> 38:28.974
regains control
of himself.

38:29.007 --> 38:30.809
...while they stockpile weapons
of mass destruction!

38:30.842 --> 38:33.311
( gavel banging )

38:34.446 --> 38:36.615
He said his father
died in Desert Storm.

38:36.648 --> 38:39.818
I need to know whether Sean
killed out of hate or revenge.

38:39.851 --> 38:41.587
Find out how
the father died.

38:42.588 --> 38:44.790
GATES:
Casey, just accept it.

38:44.823 --> 38:46.091
It's over.

38:46.124 --> 38:47.926
If you want a deal,
the answer is no.

38:47.959 --> 38:49.695
I thought you'd jump
at the chance.

38:49.728 --> 38:51.563
I wouldn't give you
the satisfaction.

38:51.597 --> 38:52.564
The jury's buying it.

38:52.598 --> 38:54.900
See, they understand hatred
'cause at one point,

38:54.933 --> 38:56.435
they've hated
someone themselves.

38:56.468 --> 38:58.136
Well, none of them
have killed three people.

38:58.169 --> 38:59.638
But they understand
the impulse,

38:59.671 --> 39:01.006
and they won't
blame Sean for his.

39:01.039 --> 39:02.941
No deal.
There's no way I acknowledge

39:02.974 --> 39:05.611
an ounce of validity
in this cockamamie defense.

39:06.612 --> 39:08.647
NOVAK:
You will realize

39:08.680 --> 39:11.082
that it's based on speculation,
on maybes and could bes.

39:11.116 --> 39:12.851
On maybes and...
( knocking on door )

39:12.884 --> 39:15.120
Practicing your summation?

39:15.153 --> 39:16.588
Yeah. It's
not working.

39:16.622 --> 39:17.856
It may not have to.

39:17.889 --> 39:19.458
I think I found what you wanted.

39:19.491 --> 39:22.594
Seth Webster--
that's Sean Webster's father--

39:22.628 --> 39:24.896
he fought in Desert Storm...

39:24.930 --> 39:26.532
didn't die there.

39:30.502 --> 39:32.504
( buzzer sounds )

39:36.041 --> 39:37.743
What's this about?

39:37.776 --> 39:39.010
You still want a deal?

39:39.044 --> 39:41.980
You've come to your senses.

39:42.013 --> 39:43.649
It's about you coming to yours.

39:43.682 --> 39:44.850
He pleads three counts,

39:44.883 --> 39:47.018
Murder Two,
consecutive sentences.

39:47.052 --> 39:49.655
Have a nice day.

39:59.164 --> 40:01.099
GATES:
Who's this?

40:03.134 --> 40:04.870
Get him out.

40:04.903 --> 40:07.773
Don't you want
to introduce Dad?

40:07.806 --> 40:09.174
Sean, what's going on?

40:09.207 --> 40:11.042
STABLER:
He never told you?

40:11.076 --> 40:13.011
His father met
an Arab woman

40:13.044 --> 40:15.914
in Kuwait,
divorced Sean's mother,

40:15.947 --> 40:17.783
remarried and moved to Detroit.

40:17.816 --> 40:20.018
You still think
it's genetics, Oliver?

40:20.051 --> 40:22.788
Why don't you
just go back

40:22.821 --> 40:24.189
to where you came from.

40:24.222 --> 40:26.858
Go back to your Arab whore.

40:26.892 --> 40:28.527
Sean, I'm sorry.

40:28.560 --> 40:30.662
What do you care, hmm?

40:30.696 --> 40:33.064
Because this is my fault.

40:33.098 --> 40:37.536
Yeah, you're damn right
it's your fault.

40:37.569 --> 40:40.806
My mom told me
that you died a hero,

40:40.839 --> 40:43.575
and you never came around
to tell me different.

40:46.111 --> 40:48.480
I go to get benefits
for college,

40:48.514 --> 40:50.949
and I find out
that he's still alive.

40:50.982 --> 40:53.819
SETH:
Sean, listen,
I wanted to see you.

40:53.852 --> 40:55.220
Your mother wouldn't let me.

40:55.253 --> 40:56.321
She had custody.

40:56.354 --> 40:59.558
She threatened that
if I even tried to come visit...

40:59.591 --> 41:00.726
Liar!

41:00.759 --> 41:03.094
You were too busy with your
half-breed kids! Admit it!

41:03.128 --> 41:06.565
She filled your head
with all this crap

41:06.598 --> 41:09.234
about Arabs
because she was angry with me.

41:09.267 --> 41:11.102
Can't you see that?

41:11.136 --> 41:13.271
She poisoned you with her hate.

41:13.304 --> 41:16.642
My mom worked her ass off
to take care of me!

41:16.675 --> 41:18.143
You never gave a damn!

41:18.176 --> 41:20.879
Oh, Sean.

41:20.912 --> 41:22.748
I hate your stinking guts!

41:22.781 --> 41:23.782
( spits )

41:23.815 --> 41:26.151
If I had a gun right now,

41:26.184 --> 41:28.720
I'd shoot you in the head,
and then I'd go back

41:28.754 --> 41:31.590
and I'd set your wife
and your bastard kids on fire!

41:31.623 --> 41:33.625
Get off me!

41:51.977 --> 41:53.879
Sean Webster wasn't born
that way.

41:53.912 --> 41:55.146
I don't believe anyone is.

41:55.180 --> 41:57.883
It takes a human being
to teach you to hate.

41:57.916 --> 42:01.152
"Some mysteries past
all understanding."

42:01.186 --> 42:02.320
Letters of St. Paul.

42:02.353 --> 42:05.891
The Muslim who Sean Webster
killed at Central Booking?

42:05.924 --> 42:07.626
He had friends.

42:07.659 --> 42:11.730
Webster was just stabbed
to death in the yard at Rikers.

